      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-xl text-gray-500 lg:mx-auto">
        Tweet-O-Matic is a twitter bot application that allows users to connect their Twitter accounts, schedule tweets and set up tweet automations for timed Twitter posts. This is a proof of concept project for the purpose of exploring new technologies.
      </p>


