            <h5 class="pt-1 ml-24 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">Omni-Auth Twitter</h5>
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-1 ml-24 text-base text-gray-500">
            The first thing you will need to do after creating your account is by attaching a Twitter account. Tweet-O-Matic uses Omni-auth Twitter to allow you to connect multiple Twitter accounts to your Tweet-O-Matic profile.
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <dt>
            <h4 class="absolute flex pt-10 items-center justify-center w-12 h-8 rounded-md  tracking-wide font-regular text-sm text-blue-500">
