            </h4>
            <h5 class="pt-1 ml-24 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">Twitter API</h5>
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-1 ml-24 text-base text-gray-500">
            Tweet-O-Matic utilizes Twitters API in conjunction with Omni-Auth Twitter to take direct actions within your Twitter account. This application uses the Twitter API to post directly to the Twitter account specified when creating either a scheduled tweet, or an automated tweet.
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <dt>
            <h4 class="absolute flex pt-10 items-center justify-center w-20 h-8 rounded-md  tracking-wide font-regular text-sm text-blue-500">
