          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-1 ml-24 text-base text-gray-500">
            Inspired by Buffer, this feature allows users to create scheduled tweets. First, select the Twitter account you would like to tweet from. Second, input the content for the scheduled tweet. That it! Input the time that you would like to schedule your tweet and you're off to the races!
          </dd>
