          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-1 ml-24 text-base text-gray-500">
            This is the most exciting feature by far. Tweet Automations allow users to create their very own Twitter Bots! First, select the Twitter account you would like to tweet from. Second, pick a content category. Last, select the length of time you want your new twitter bot to run for. You've done it!
          </dd>
